<core:View height="100%" 
  xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" 
  xmlns="sap.m" 
  xmlns:tnt="sap.tnt" 
  xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout" 
  xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" 
  xmlns:app="http://schemas.sap.com/sapui5/extension/sap.ui.core.CustomData/1" controllerName="UI5FioriForTools.controller.init" id="app">
  <tnt:ToolPage id="rootApp">
    <tnt:header>
      <tnt:ToolHeader>
        <Image width="48px" src="https://cockpit.hanatrial.ondemand.com/~1571908964000~/images/sap_logo.svg">
        </Image>
        <Label text="SAP Cloud Platform Cockpit" class="text-color-header" design="Bold" />
        <ToolbarSpacer/>
          <Button icon="sap-icon://travel-request" type="Transparent">
            <layoutData>
              <OverflowToolbarLayoutData priority="NeverOverflow" />
            </layoutData>
          </Button>        	
          <Button text="Alan Smith" type="Transparent" press="onUserNamePress">
            <layoutData>
              <OverflowToolbarLayoutData priority="NeverOverflow" />
            </layoutData>
          </Button>
          <Button icon="sap-icon://sys-help" type="Transparent">
            <layoutData>
              <OverflowToolbarLayoutData priority="NeverOverflow" />
            </layoutData>
          </Button>
      </tnt:ToolHeader>
    </tnt:header>
    <tnt:mainContents>
      <App id="MainContainer"/>
    </tnt:mainContents>
  </tnt:ToolPage>
</core:View>